<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es" style="scroll-behavior: smooth;">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>IAExpertos.org - Soluciones de IA para tu Empresa</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;600;700;800&family=Open+Sans:wght@300;400;600;700&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #4158D0 0%, #764BA2 50%, #C850C0 100%);
      --secondary-gradient: linear-gradient(90deg, #FF6B6B 0%, #FFA500 100%);
      --text-gradient: linear-gradient(45deg, #FFD700, #FF69B4, #87CEFA);
      --purple-glow: 0 0 15px rgba(114, 9, 183, 0.4);
      --blue-glow: 0 0 15px rgba(65, 88, 208, 0.4);
    }
    body {
      font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
      background: var(--primary-gradient);
      color: #ffffff;
      line-height: 1.8;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }
    h1, h2, h3, h4 {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding-left: 1rem;
      padding-right: 1rem;
    }
    @media (min-width: 640px) {
      .container {
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
        padding-right: 1.5rem;
      }
    }
    .header-bg {
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.75);
      backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
    }
    .card {
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
      transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275), box-shadow 0.4s ease;
    }
    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35), var(--purple-glow);
      border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    }
    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--secondary-gradient);
      transition: all 0.4s ease;
      text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }
    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #FFA500 0%, #FF6B6B 100%);
      transform: translateY(-3px) scale(1.03);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.6);
    }
    .text-gradient {
      background: var(--text-gradient);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }
    .fade-in {
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeIn 1.2s ease-out forwards;
      animation-delay: 0.2s;
    }
    .slide-up {
      transform: translateY(30px);
      transition: transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275), opacity 0.8s ease;
    }
    .slide-up.active {
      transform: translateY(0);
      opacity: 1;
    }
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      to { opacity: 1; }
    }
    .full-cover-section {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 500px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      background-attachment: fixed;
    }
    .full-cover-overlay {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 0, 30, 0.85), rgba(65, 88, 208, 0.6));
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .full-cover-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .service-image {
      width: 100%;
      height: 250px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 0.75rem 0.75rem 0 0;
      transition: transform 0.5s ease;
      filter: brightness(0.9);
    }
    .card:hover .service-image {
      transform: scale(1.05);
      filter: brightness(1);
    }
    .circular-image {
      width: 140px;
      height: 140px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      object-fit: cover;
      border: 3px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      transition: transform 0.5s ease, box-shadow 0.5s ease;
    }
    .circular-image:hover {
      transform: scale(1.1);
      border-color: rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.6);
      box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.3), var(--purple-glow);
    }
    .footer-bg {
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }
    .form-control {
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      color: #ffffff;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      width: 100%;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .form-control::placeholder {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    }
    .form-control:focus {
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
      border-color: #FFD700;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.25), var(--blue-glow);
      outline: none;
    }
    .btn {
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .btn-lg {
      padding: 16px 32px;
      font-size: 16px;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
    .btn-dark {
      background: var(--secondary-gradient);
      color: white;
    }
    .btn-dark:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.6);
    }
    .btn-block {
      width: 100%;
      display: block;
    }
    .feature-card {
      height: 100%;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .feature-card-content {
      flex-grow: 1;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .feature-card-content a {
      margin-top: auto;
    }
    .hero-section {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 90vh;
      overflow: hidden;
      background-image: url('https://img.freepik.com/premium-vector/ai-technology-concept-artificial-intelligence-blue-purple-dots-lines-digital-communication-science-networks_322958-1111.jpg');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      background-attachment: fixed;
    }
    .hero-overlay {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 0, 30, 0.8), rgba(65, 88, 208, 0.6));
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .particles {
      position: absolute;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      z-index: 2;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .particle {
      position: absolute;
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
      border-radius: 50%;
      animation: float 10s infinite ease-in-out;
    }
    @keyframes float {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) translateX(0) rotate(0deg); opacity: 0.6; }
      25% { transform: translateY(-30px) translateX(15px) rotate(90deg); opacity: 1; }
      50% { transform: translateY(-15px) translateX(30px) rotate(180deg); opacity: 0.8; }
      75% { transform: translateY(30px) translateX(-15px) rotate(270deg); opacity: 1; }
    }
    .ai-logo {
      width: 70px;
      height: 70px;
      position: relative;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4158D0 0%, #764BA2 100%);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3), var(--purple-glow);
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: transform 0.4s ease, box-shadow 0.4s ease;
    }
    .ai-logo:hover {
      transform: rotate(15deg) scale(1.05);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4), var(--blue-glow);
    }
    .ai-logo-inner {
      position: relative;
      width: 80%;
      height: 80%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
      backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
    }
    .ai-logo-icon {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: white;
      text-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }
    .logo-text {
      margin-left: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7EEAFD 0%, #4EA8F3 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
    .stat-number {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      background: var(--text-gradient);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }
    .testimonial-card {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .testimonial-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3) 0%, rgba(118, 75, 162, 0.3) 100%);
      z-index: -1;
    }
    .testimonial-card::after {
      content: '\f10d';
      font-family: 'Font Awesome 6 Free';
      font-weight: 900;
      position: absolute;
      top: 10px;
      right: 15px;
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero-title {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
      }
      .stat-number {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
      }
      .full-cover-section, .hero-section {
        background-attachment: scroll;
      }
    }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar {
      width: 8px;
    }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    }
    @media print {
      .hero-section, .full-cover-section {
        background-attachment: scroll !important;
      }
      .fade-in {
        opacity: 1 !important;
        animation: none !important;
      }
      .card:hover {
        transform: none !important;
      }
    }
    #mensaje-exito {
      color: #a7f3d0;
      background-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);
      padding: 1rem;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      margin-top: 1em;
      text-align: center;
      transform: translateY(20px);
      opacity: 0;
      transition: all 0.5s ease;
    }
    #mensaje-exito.show {
      transform: translateY(0);
      opacity: 1;
    }
    
    /* Chatbot Styles */
    .chatbot-container {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 25px;
      right: 25px;
      z-index: 1000;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    }
    .chatbot-toggle {
      width: 65px;
      height: 65px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4158D0 0%, #C850C0 100%);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3), var(--purple-glow);
      transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
    }
    .chatbot-toggle:hover {
      transform: scale(1.1) rotate(10deg);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4), var(--blue-glow);
    }
    .chatbot-toggle i {
      font-size: 28px;
      color: white;
      text-shadow: 0 2px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }
    .chatbot-window {
      width: 370px;
      max-width: 90vw;
      height: 500px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25), var(--purple-glow);
      overflow: hidden;
      display: none;
      flex-direction: column;
      transform: translateY(30px);
      transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
      opacity: 0;
    }
    .chatbot-window.active {
      display: flex;
      transform: translateY(0);
      opacity: 1;
    }
    .chatbot-header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4158D0 0%, #C850C0 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 18px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .chatbot-header h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 18px;
      text-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }
    .chatbot-close {
      background: none;
      border: none;
      color: white;
      font-size: 22px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }
    .chatbot-close:hover {
      transform: rotate(90deg);
    }
    .chatbot-messages {
      flex-grow: 1;
      padding: 18px;
      overflow-y: auto;
      background: #f8f9fa;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .message {
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      max-width: 85%;
      padding: 12px 18px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      position: relative;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      animation: messageAppear 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
    }
    @keyframes messageAppear {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(10px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }
    .bot-message {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #e9ecef, #dee2e6);
      color: #333;
      border-top-left-radius: 5px;
      align-self: flex-start;
    }
    .user-message {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4158D0 0%, #C850C0 100%);
      color: white;
      border-top-right-radius: 5px;
      margin-left: auto;
    }
    .chatbot-input {
      display: flex;
      padding: 15px;
      background: white;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
    }
    .chatbot-input input {
      flex-grow: 1;
      padding: 12px 18px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 25px;
      outline: none;
      font-size: 15px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .chatbot-input input:focus {
      border-color: #4158D0;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(65, 88, 208, 0.2);
    }
    .chatbot-input button {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4158D0 0%, #C850C0 100%);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 50%;
      width: 45px;
      height: 45px;
      margin-left: 12px;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .chatbot-input button:hover {
      transform: scale(1.1);
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(65, 88, 208, 0.4);
    }
    .typing-indicator {
      display: flex;
      padding: 10px 15px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #e9ecef, #dee2e6);
      border-radius: 18px;
      width: fit-content;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .typing-indicator span {
      height: 8px;
      width: 8px;
      background: #6c757d;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 0 3px;
      animation: typing 1.4s infinite ease-in-out;
    }
    .typing-indicator span:nth-child(2) {
      animation-delay: 0.2s;
    }
    .typing-indicator span:nth-child(3) {
      animation-delay: 0.4s;
    }
    @keyframes typing {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); background: #adb5bd; }
      50% { transform: translateY(-5px); background: #6c757d; }
    }
    .quick-replies {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }
    .quick-reply {
      background: white;
      color: #4158D0;
      border: 1px solid #4158D0;
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 6px 14px;
      font-size: 13px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .quick-reply:hover {
      background: #4158D0;
      color: white;
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }
    
    /* Páginas y términos legales */
    .legal-page {
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
      color: #333;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 40px auto;
    }
    .legal-page h2 {
      color: #4158D0;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .legal-page h3 {
      color: #764BA2;
      margin-top: 25px;
    }
    
    /* Enhanced animations */
    .pulse {
      animation: pulse 2s infinite;
    }
    @keyframes pulse {
      0% { transform: scale(1); }
      50% { transform: scale(1.05); }
      100% { transform: scale(1); }
    }
    .glow {
      animation: glow 2s infinite alternate;
    }
    @keyframes glow {
      from { box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(65, 88, 208, 0.3); }
      to { box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(200, 80, 192, 0.6); }
    }
    .hover-lift {
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }
    .hover-lift:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }
    
    /* Floating animated circles */
    .floating-circles {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      z-index: 0;
    }
    .circle {
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(65, 88, 208, 0.2), rgba(200, 80, 192, 0.2));
      backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
      animation: floatingCircle 15s infinite linear;
    }
    @keyframes floatingCircle {
      0% { transform: translate(0, 0) rotate(0deg); opacity: 0.3; }
      25% { transform: translate(50px, -30px) rotate(90deg); opacity: 0.5; }
      50% { transform: translate(100px, 0) rotate(180deg); opacity: 0.3; }
      75% { transform: translate(50px, 30px) rotate(270deg); opacity: 0.5; }
      100% { transform: translate(0, 0) rotate(360deg); opacity: 0.3; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="antialiased">
  <header class="header-bg py-4 sm:py-5 sticky top-0 z-50 rounded-b-lg shadow-lg">
    <div class="container flex justify-between items-center">
      <a href="#" class="flex items-center group">
        <div class="ai-logo group-hover:rotate-12 transition-transform duration-300">
          <div class="ai-logo-inner">
            <div class="ai-logo-icon">AI</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <span class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl logo-text hidden md:block tracking-wide group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">IAExpertos.org</span>
      </a>
      <nav class="flex space-x-2 sm:space-x-3 md:space-x-6">
        <a href="#soluciones" class="text-sm sm:text-base text-white hover:text-yellow-300 transition duration-300 ease-in-out font-semibold px-1 sm:px-2 hover:-translate-y-1 inline-flex items-center">
          <i class="fas fa-lightbulb mr-1"></i> <span class="border-b border-transparent hover:border-yellow-300">Soluciones</span>
        </a>
        <a href="#servicios" class="text-sm sm:text-base text-white hover:text-yellow-300 transition duration-300 ease-in-out font-semibold px-1 sm:px-2 hover:-translate-y-1 inline-flex items-center">
          <i class="fas fa-cogs mr-1"></i> <span class="border-b border-transparent hover:border-yellow-300">Servicios</span>
        </a>
        <a href="#clientes" class="text-sm sm:text-base text-white hover:text-yellow-300 transition duration-300 ease-in-out font-semibold px-1 sm:px-2 hover:-translate-y-1 inline-flex items-center">
          <i class="fas fa-star mr-1"></i> <span class="border-b border-transparent hover:border-yellow-300">Clientes</span>
        </a>
        <a href="#contacto" class="text-sm sm:text-base text-white hover:text-yellow-300 transition duration-300 ease-in-out font-semibold px-1 sm:px-2 hover:-translate-y-1 inline-flex items-center">
          <i class="fas fa-envelope mr-1"></i> <span class="border-b border-transparent hover:border-yellow-300">Contacto</span>
        </a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero-section flex items-center justify-center py-20 text-center p-4 sm:p-6">
      <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
      <div class="floating-circles" id="floating-circles"></div>
      <div class="particles" id="particles"></div>
      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto fade-in">
        <div class="mb-8 flex justify-center">
          <div class="w-28 h-28 md:w-36 md:h-36 rounded-full bg-blue-500 bg-opacity-30 flex items-center justify-center p-3 glow">
            <div class="ai-logo pulse" style="width: 100%; height: 100%;">
              <div class="ai-logo-inner">
                <div class="ai-logo-icon" style="font-size: 2.8rem;">AI</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl xs:text-5xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold leading-tight mb-6 sm:mb-8 text-gradient drop-shadow-xl">
          Soluciones IA para Potenciar tu Empresa
        </h1>
        <p class="text-base xs:text-lg sm:text-xl lg:text-2xl mb-8 sm:mb-10 text-white text-opacity-90 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Desbloquea el futuro de tu negocio con inteligencia artificial de vanguardia. En IAExpertos.org, somos tu equipo de especialistas en IA, dedicados a ofrecerte soluciones personalizadas que marcan la diferencia.
        </p>
